[TITLE]
FILLTIME / DRAINTIME rule premises (thresholds in hours, EPANET convention)

[JUNCTIONS]
J1    0    50

[RESERVOIRS]
R1    0

[TANKS]
T1    100   5     0    10   50    0

[PIPES]
P1    R1    J1    1000    12    100    0    Open
P2    J1    T1    500     12    100    0    Open

[PUMPS]
PMP1    R1    J1    HEAD C1

[CURVES]
C1    0       300
C1    1000    200

[RULES]
RULE 1
IF NODE T1 FILLTIME > 2
THEN LINK PMP1 STATUS IS OPEN
PRIORITY 2

RULE 2
IF NODE T1 DRAINTIME < 0.5
THEN LINK PMP1 STATUS IS OPEN
PRIORITY 1

[OPTIONS]
Units    GPM
Headloss    H-W

[TIMES]
Duration    12:00
Hydraulic Timestep    1:00
Report Timestep    1:00

[END]
